com.roscopeco.moxy.api

Interface InvocationSupplier<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Return type of the method to be invoked.
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface InvocationSupplier<T>
    Functional interface used to run monitored method invocations (e.g. for when(...) and assertMock(...)) with return type T.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ross Bamford <roscopeco AT gmail DOT com>
